items.en: If you have a Stand power, pressing %s will switch Stand overlay UI; %s does the same for your other power (Vampirism/Hamon).
items.zh: 如果你拥有替身能力, 按下%s帮助你切换到替身UI面板,帮助你切换替身能力和攻击方式; %s键可以切换其他的UI面板 (比如吸血鬼/『波纹』).

items.en: With an overlay on, you'll see two new hotbars for attacks and abilities available to you in this mode. While holding %s or %s, your 1-9 keys and mouse wheel can be used to choose an attack or ability respectively. Empty slots are for attacks/abilities which you haven't yet unlocked and therefore are skipped over.
items.zh: 打开UI面板后, 您会看到在此面板下左上角会出现两个新快捷栏，分别是攻击和能力。按住%s或%s键时，您的1-9键和鼠标滚轮可用于分别切换攻击和能力释放方式。空槽是您尚未解锁的攻击/能力，因此会被跳过。

items.en: You can perform the attack you have selected by pressing %1$s. Similarly, to use the selected ability, press %2$s. Performing an attack/ability will (in most cases) cancel vanilla attack/interaction.
items.zh: 您可以按下%1$s键帮助你切换攻击方式。同理，如果您可以通过按下%2$s切换能力，使用攻击/能力将（在大多数情况下）取消攻击/能力。

items.en: If you have a summonable Stand, press %s to summon/unsummon it. If the Stand you have summoned can be controlled manually (i.e. most of the Stands which take form of an entity), pressing %s will switch between normal mode and manual control mode, in which you can directly control your Stand's movements.
items.zh: 如果你拥有一个可以完全显露的替身， 请按下%s来进行释放/收回。如果您释放的替身可以远程控制（以完全体形式显露的替身）按下%s键可以在正常跟随和远程控制来回切换，远程控制时可以控制替身的进行移动.

items.en: Pressing %s will open a window where you can rearrange the moves in the HUD, as well as add extra keybinds for each individual move.

In JJBA, Hamon is a form of energy produced by trained fighters via breathing. This energy has properties similar to sunlight's, making it fatal to zombies, vampires, and Pillar Men. In this mod it is one of the unique powers you can get.
items.zh: 在JJBA中，波纹是一种通过呼吸训练产生的能量形式。这种能量具有类似阳光的特性，对僵尸、吸血鬼和柱之男具有致命效果。在本模组中，它是你可以获得的一种独特能力。

items.en: To use Hamon effectively, you have to manage your breath, represented by %s in the left upper corner.
items.zh: 要有效地使用波纹，你需要管理你的呼吸，在左上角由 %s 表示。

items.en: All the Hamon moves, like Overdrive, Healing, or any other ones you unlock, spend %s.
items.zh: 所有波纹招式，如过载、治疗或其他你解锁的招式，都会消耗 %s。

items.en: Hamon energy is filled by using the special %s, bound to Middle Mouse Button by default.
items.zh: 波纹能量可以通过使用特殊的 %s 来补充，默认绑定在鼠标中键。

items.en: The translucent part of the bar is referred to as %s. If you do not refill Hamon energy, breath stability is used up instead. Spending it makes your Hamon weaker and lowers the energy cap for a little while.
items.zh: 能量条的半透明部分称为 %s。如果你不补充波纹能量，而是消耗它，你的波纹会变弱，并在短时间内降低能量上限。

items.en: If you manage your Hamon energy well, you will not have to worry about that.
items.zh: 如果你的波纹能量管理得当，你就不必担心这个问题。

items.en: With proper training you can become a stronger Hamon warrior. The next tab shows your Hamon stats and explains the training process.
items.zh: 通过适当的训练，你可以成为更强的波纹战士。下一个标签页显示你的波纹统计数据并解释训练过程。

items.en: Use Hamon Breath to breathe through the mask
items.zh: 使用波纹呼吸通过面具呼吸

items.en: Determines the power of your Hamon attacks. Is trained by using Hamon attacks.
items.zh: 决定你波纹攻击的威力。通过使用波纹攻击进行训练。

items.en: Determines the amount of Hamon energy spent and efficiency of your Hamon abilities. Is trained by using Hamon abilities.
items.zh: 决定消耗的波纹能量以及波纹能力的效率。通过使用波纹能力进行训练。

items.en: The level won't increase unless you increase your breathing training level
items.zh: 除非提高呼吸训练等级，否则该等级不会提升
你的 %s 已提升至 %s 级！

items.en: This stat increases your breathing ability as well as your physical condition.
items.zh: 此属性会提高你的呼吸能力以及身体状况。

items.en: You'll need to constantly train it in order to make progress in learning Hamon.
items.zh: 为了在学习波纹方面取得进步，你需要不断训练它。

items.en: To train your breathing, you have to complete these exercises daily. Complete at least 3 of them each day for maximum results. It is also recommended to craft and wear a %s if you want to commit to your Hamon training.
items.zh: 要训练你的呼吸，你必须每天完成这些练习。每天至少完成其中三项以获得最大效果。如果你想全身心投入波纹训练，也建议制作并穿戴 %s。

items.en: The training level will slowly decrease if you stop doing the exercises!
items.zh: 如果你停止进行练习，训练等级会缓慢下降！

items.en: You won't be able to increase your Hamon Strength/Hamon Control %s or more levels above the breathing training level.
items.zh: 你无法将你的波纹力量/波纹控制提升到比呼吸训练等级高 %s 或更多的等级。

items.en: Bonus %s points for previous consecutive training days

items.en: Meditating also helps restore breath stability faster

items.zh: 适合战斗的能力：各种波纹攻击或增强机动性的招式。每提升 5 级波纹力量，你将获得一个技能点，可在此面板中学习一项能力。

items.en: Hamon Abilities other than combat moves. Most of these are defensive capabilities or utility skills. For each 5 levels of Hamon Control you get a skill point to learn a skill from this tab.
items.zh: 除战斗招式外的波纹能力。大部分是防御能力或实用技能。每提升 5 级波纹控制，你将获得一个技能点，可在此面板中学习一项能力。

items.en: The most basic application of Hamon. The user channels the Hamon energy through their fist, and deals damage either with a direct punch, or by transmitting the energy through a solid or liquid material.
items.zh: 波纹最基础的应用。使用者通过拳头传导波纹能量，并直接通过拳击、固体或液体来造成伤害。

items.en: Various materials can be imbued with Hamon energy. Living organisms can retain the energy for a longer time.
items.zh: 各种物质都可以被灌注波纹能量。生物体可以更长时间地保留能量。

items.en: Hamon can help its user exceed the limits of their movement capabilities and attack range.
items.zh: 波纹能量可以帮助使用者超越身体机能的限制，增强速度和攻击范围。

items.en: Hamon energy can speed up the regeneration of a living body.
items.zh: 波纹能量蕴含着生命力，可以加速生物体的再生。

items.en: Attractant and repellent Hamon are two opposite types of Hamon energy, each having their special use cases.
items.zh: 吸引与排斥是两种相反的波纹能量，各有其特殊用途。

items.en: Hamon energy can affect organisms by vibrating the water inside their bodies.
items.zh: 波纹能量可以通过震动生物体内的水分来影响生物。

items.en: The user's unarmed punches deal additional Hamon damage. Hamon is especially effective against undead creatures.
items.zh: 玩家空手时的拳击会造成额外的波纹伤害，对不死生物尤为有效！

items.en: Shift variation - Hamon Beat - is a stronger attack with extra knockback.
items.zh: Shift 变招 - 波纹重击 - 是一个更强的攻击，并附带击退效果。

items.en: Applying this attack to a wall or floor creates a wave of Hamon energy, which damages mobs and players in the area.\nWhen used on the floor, this creates a narrower wave, or, when the attack is charged for longer, an area of effect.
items.zh: 向墙壁或地面施加此攻击，会产生波纹能量波，对区域内的生物造成伤害。攻击地面时，波纹会形成一条更窄的波；蓄力更长时间时，会形成一个范围效果。

items.en: While underwater, the user can transfer a powerful wave of Hamon energy through water.
items.zh: 在水下时，玩家可以释放出强大的波纹能量。

items.en: A Hamon-charged heavy blow. By charging the attack for longer, the user can channel more Hamon energy into the punch to deal a lot of damage.
items.zh: 附带波纹能量的重击。通过延长蓄力时间，玩家能够将更多的波纹能量汇聚于拳头，造成大量伤害。

items.en: Snowballs, eggs and splash water bottles the user throws inflict additional Hamon damage.
items.zh: 玩家投掷的雪球、鸡蛋和水瓶等物品将附带波纹伤害。

items.en: The user temporarily charges a block of a plant with Hamon. While it's charged, mobs and players will take Hamon damage upon touching it.
items.zh: 玩家暂时用波纹为植物方块充能。充能期间，靠近它的生物会受到波纹伤害。

items.en: Allows the user to charge living mobs and players with Hamon.
items.zh: 允许玩家向生物和海龟蛋灌注波纹。

items.en: When throwing out a plant, the user charges it with Hamon. Mobs and players getting too close to it will take Hamon damage.
items.zh: 玩家扔出植物类物品时，会向其灌注波纹，靠近的生物会受到波纹伤害。

items.en: Arrows and tridents the user shoots inflict additional Hamon damage.
items.zh: 玩家发射的箭矢和三叉戟将造成额外的波纹伤害。

items.en: Extends the user's arm, allowing them to punch an enemy from longer distance, additionally dealing Hamon damage.
items.zh: 通过关节脱臼来延长攻击距离，附带波纹伤害。

items.en: Allows the user to leap forward by jumping while sneaking.
items.zh: 允许玩家在潜行时按下跳跃键向前飞跃。

items.en: Gives the user Speed and Haste effects for a short amount of time.
items.zh: 短时间内为玩家提供速度和急迫效果。

items.en: Speed Boost ability gives stronger effects. Leap's strength is increased. Maximum speed boost summons the user's afterimages.
items.zh: 身体加速控制提供更强的加速效果并产生残影；飞跃效果增强。

items.en: Allows the user to heal others with Healing ability while sneaking.
items.zh: 允许玩家在潜行时，通过治疗能力治疗他人。

items.en: The Healing ability can apply bone meal effect.
items.zh: 治疗能力对植物使用时，可起到类似于骨粉的作用。

items.en: The user's Healing ability also removes Poison, Hunger, Wither and Nausea effects.
items.zh: 玩家的治疗能力将帮助目标排出体内的毒素（持续减少剧毒、饥饿、凋零和反胃效果的持续时间）。

items.en: Lets the user adhere to a vertical surface and climb it.
items.zh: 允许玩家使用波纹附着在方块表面进行攀爬。

items.en: Allows the user to freely walk on a liquid surface. Press double Shift to disable.
items.zh: 允许玩家在液体表面行走，双击 Shift 键可停止使用。

items.en: Turns a block of leaves into a hang glider. If not continuously charged with Hamon energy, the glider will disintegrate.
items.zh: 将一块树叶变成滑翔伞；如果不持续为树叶充能波纹，滑翔伞将解体。

items.en: Creates a projectile reflecting barrier in front of the user.
items.zh: 在玩家前方创建一个防护壁，可反弹任何投掷物。

items.en: Creates a Hamon-charged coating on the surface of the user's body, reducing the incoming physical damage.
items.zh: 在身体表面形成一层排斥波纹，对来袭的物体产生排斥并降低受到的物理伤害。

items.en: Gives entities around the user Glowing effect.
items.zh: 为周围实体提供发光效果。

items.en: The user temporarily tames a tameable animal.
items.zh: 允许玩家临时驯服一只可驯服的生物。

items.en: The user applies a Hamon charge directly to a living creature's head, incapacitating them for a short time. The shock wears off if the target takes damage.
items.zh: 向生物头部施加波纹，使其短时间失去行动能力；但若目标受到伤害，痉挛效果将解除。

items.en: Whenever the user attack an undead with Hamon, it continues spreading through the target's body, weakening it and slowing down its regeneration.
items.zh: 玩家用波纹攻击亡灵生物时，波纹会持续在其体内扩散，造成额外伤害。

items.en: Choosing this technique will also increase the efficiency of the following skills:
items.zh: 选择此技巧将提升以下技能分支的效率：

items.en: Choose carefully! You won't be able to change your technique unless you fully abandon the Hamon training and start over.
items.zh: 请谨慎选择！除非你完全放弃波纹训练并从头开始，否则你将无法更改技巧！

items.en: Please note that some of the skills are undergoing a rework.
items.zh: 请注意：部分技能正在重做。
你的波纹训练效率翻倍。

items.en: A special type of Sunlight Yellow Overdrive attack that sets the target on fire.
items.zh: 山吹色波纹疾走的变种，命中目标可造成点燃效果。

items.en: You can perform Overdrive attack with a weapon or a tool.\nWithout a weapon, the regular Overdrive deals more damage to targets with armor or an equipped melee weapon.
items.zh: 你可以使用武器或工具进行波纹疾走攻击。在没有武器的情况下，普通波纹疾走对身着护甲或持有近战武器的目标造成更高伤害。

items.en: You unleash a barrage of rapid Overdrive attacks.
items.zh: 你发动一系列快速的波纹疾走攻击。

items.en: A more powerful variation of Overdrive Barrage, followed by a devastating finishing punch. Takes a few seconds to charge.
Infuse a bottle of liquid with Hamon and shoot the liquid out at high speed. In addition to Hamon damage, the potion's effect is applied to the target.
items.zh: 向药水中灌注波纹，然后高速投掷。除了波纹伤害外，药水的效果也会施加到目标身上。

items.en: You charge forward, hitting all enemies on your way with your knee, additionally dealing Hamon damage to them.
items.zh: 向前冲锋，用膝盖攻击途中的所有敌人，并造成额外波纹伤害。

items.en: By spinning at high speed, you deal Hamon damage to the enemies around you. This attack is especially deadly while falling.
items.zh: 通过高速旋转，对周围的敌人造成波纹伤害。在下坠时使用尤为致命。

items.en: When you die, you transfer all of your life energy (Hamon Strength and Control levels) to a nearby Hamon User.
items.zh: 当你死亡时，你将所有生命能量（波纹力量和控制等级）转移给附近的一名波纹使用者。

items.en: Allows you to use a pair of clackers as a Hamon-infused melee weapon or charge and throw it at the opponent at high speed.
items.zh: 允许你将一对钢珠旋风作为灌注波纹的近战武器，或高速投掷给对手。

items.en: Right-clicking a string temporarily turns connected strings into a Hamon-charged cobweb. While sneaking, you automatically place a string from your hotbar.
items.zh: 右键单击线会暂时将连接的线转换为缠绕波纹的线网。潜行时，你会自动放置一根热键栏中的线。

items.en: When you are about to die, you will avoid death and gain Invisibility effect (once an in-game day).\nYour next words: \"What does it have to do with Hamon?\"
items.zh: 当你即将死亡时，你会规避死亡并获得短暂隐形效果（游戏中每天一次）。\n你的下一句话是：“这个能力和波纹有什么关系？”

items.en: You get into a defensive stance and swing with both elbows. If attacked in melee during a specific timing window, your strike parries the attack, dealing devastating amount of Hamon damage and extra knockback.
items.zh: 进入防御姿态并用双肘挥击。在特定时机被近战攻击命中时，你的攻击会招架住攻击，造成毁灭性的波纹伤害和额外的击退。

items.en: All bubble attacks consume soap, which comes in form of Soap Solution bottles, or Soap Coated Gloves.
items.zh: 所有泡泡攻击都需要使用泡泡水或泡泡手套。

items.en: Shoot a barrage of Hamon-charged bubbles.
Shoot out disc-shaped bubbles, which move at a high velocity. Gliding variation bubbles are more precise and, instead of hitting the ground, continue to glide above it.
items.zh: 发射圆盘状的泡沫，以高速移动。滑动泡沫更精准，撞击地面时不会破碎，而是继续在地面上滑动。

items.en: Shoot a large-sized bubble, which traps its target for a few seconds.
items.zh: 发射一个巨大的泡泡，将目标困住几秒钟。

items.en: When you die, you put your life energy (Hamon Strength and Control levels) into a bubble, from which it can be transferred to another Hamon user.
items.zh: 当你死亡时，你将生命能量（波纹力量和控制等级）放入一个血泡泡中，它可以转移给附近的另一位波纹使用者。

items.en: You can instantly charge an Aja Stone with Hamon. When using a regular Aja Stone, you have a small chance to turn it into Super Aja.
items.zh: 你可以用波纹立即为艾哲红石充能；使用普通艾哲红石时，你有几率将其转化为超级艾哲红石。
附着波纹的围巾（开发中）

items.en: You get a scarf which, when worn, reduces Hamon energy spent and absorbs Hamon damage. You can use it as a Hamon-conductive melee weapon or swing it to cover a larger area of targets.
items.zh: 获得一条围巾，佩戴时可减少波纹能量消耗并吸收波纹伤害。可作为传导波纹的近战武器，或挥舞进行大范围攻击。

items.en: When getting attacked while wearing the scarf, you jump over the attacker using the scarf and deal Hamon damage to them (has a cooldown). Attacking with the scarf while sneaking ensnares the target.
items.zh: 佩戴围巾时受到攻击，你会用围巾跳过攻击者并造成波纹伤害（有冷却）。潜行时挥舞围巾可缠住目标。

items.en: You feel sleepy. Maybe sleeping a bit will finish this nightmare...
items.zh: 你感到困乏了，也许睡一觉就能结束这场噩梦……
炎之流法：巨型车轮囚笼

items.zh: 光之流法：辉彩骨刃连击

of.options.ADVANCED_TOOLTIPS.tooltip.6=(id, source, default value).

of.options.DROPPED_ITEMS=Dropped Items
of.options.DROPPED_ITEMS.tooltip.1=Dropped Items
of.options.DROPPED_ITEMS.tooltip.2=  Default - as set by setting Graphics
of.options.DROPPED_ITEMS.tooltip.3=  Fast - 2D dropped items (faster)
of.options.DROPPED_ITEMS.tooltip.4=  Fancy - 3D dropped items (slower)

options.entityShadows.tooltip.1=Entity Shadows
options.entityShadows.tooltip.2=  ON - show entity shadows
options.entityShadows.tooltip.3=  OFF - do not show entity shadows

of.options.VIGNETTE=Vignette
of.options.VIGNETTE.tooltip.1=Visual effect which slightly darkens the screen corners
of.options.VIGNETTE.tooltip.2=  Default - as set by the setting Graphics (default)
of.options.VIGNETTE.tooltip.3=  Fast - vignette disabled (faster)
of.options.VIGNETTE.tooltip.4=  Fancy - vignette enabled (slower)
of.options.VIGNETTE.tooltip.5=The vignette may have a significant effect on the FPS,
of.options.VIGNETTE.tooltip.6=especially when playing fullscreen.
of.options.VIGNETTE.tooltip.7=The vignette effect is very subtle and can safely
of.options.VIGNETTE.tooltip.8=be disabled.

of.options.DYNAMIC_FOV=Dynamic FOV
of.options.DYNAMIC_FOV.tooltip.1=Dynamic FOV
of.options.DYNAMIC_FOV.tooltip.2=  ON - enable dynamic FOV (default)
of.options.DYNAMIC_FOV.tooltip.3=  OFF - disable dynamic FOV
of.options.DYNAMIC_FOV.tooltip.4=Changes the field of view (FOV) when flying, sprinting 
of.options.DYNAMIC_FOV.tooltip.5=or pulling a bow.

of.options.DYNAMIC_LIGHTS=Dynamic Lights
of.options.DYNAMIC_LIGHTS.tooltip.1=Dynamic Lights
of.options.DYNAMIC_LIGHTS.tooltip.2=  OFF - no dynamic lights (default)
of.options.DYNAMIC_LIGHTS.tooltip.3=  Fast - fast dynamic lights (updated every 500ms)
of.options.DYNAMIC_LIGHTS.tooltip.4=  Fancy - fancy dynamic lights (updated in real-time)
of.options.DYNAMIC_LIGHTS.tooltip.5=Enables light emitting items (torch, glowstone, etc.)
of.options.DYNAMIC_LIGHTS.tooltip.6=to illuminate everything around them when held in hand,
of.options.DYNAMIC_LIGHTS.tooltip.7=equipped by other player or dropped on the ground.

options.biomeBlendRadius.tooltip.1=Smooths the color transition between biomes
options.biomeBlendRadius.tooltip.2=  OFF - no blending (fastest)
options.biomeBlendRadius.tooltip.3=  5x5 - normal blending (default)
options.biomeBlendRadius.tooltip.4=  15x15 - maximal blending (slowest)
options.biomeBlendRadius.tooltip.5=Higher values may generate significant lag spikes
options.biomeBlendRadius.tooltip.6=and slow down the chunk loading speed.

# Performance

of.options.SMOOTH_FPS=Smooth FPS
of.options.SMOOTH_FPS.tooltip.1=Stabilizes FPS by flushing the graphic driver buffers.
of.options.SMOOTH_FPS.tooltip.2=  OFF - no stabilization, FPS may fluctuate
of.options.SMOOTH_FPS.tooltip.3=  ON - FPS stabilization
of.options.SMOOTH_FPS.tooltip.4=This option is graphics driver dependant and its effect
of.options.SMOOTH_FPS.tooltip.5=is not always visible.

of.options.SMOOTH_WORLD=Smooth World
of.options.SMOOTH_WORLD.tooltip.1=Removes lag spikes caused by the internal server.
of.options.SMOOTH_WORLD.tooltip.2=  OFF - no stabilization, FPS may fluctuate
of.options.SMOOTH_WORLD.tooltip.3=  ON - FPS stabilization
of.options.SMOOTH_WORLD.tooltip.4=Stabilizes FPS by distributing the internal server load.
of.options.SMOOTH_WORLD.tooltip.5=Effective only for local worlds (single player).

of.options.FAST_RENDER=Fast Render
of.options.FAST_RENDER.tooltip.1=Fast Render
of.options.FAST_RENDER.tooltip.2= OFF - standard rendering (default)
of.options.FAST_RENDER.tooltip.3= ON - optimized rendering (faster)
of.options.FAST_RENDER.tooltip.4=Uses optimized rendering algorithm which decreases
of.options.FAST_RENDER.tooltip.5=the CPU load and may substantially increase the FPS.
of.options.FAST_RENDER.tooltip.6=This option can conflict with some mods.

of.options.FAST_MATH=Fast Math
of.options.FAST_MATH.tooltip.1=Fast Math
of.options.FAST_MATH.tooltip.2= OFF - standard math (default)
of.options.FAST_MATH.tooltip.3= ON - faster math
of.options.FAST_MATH.tooltip.4=Uses optimized sin() and cos() functions which can
of.options.FAST_MATH.tooltip.5=better utilize the CPU cache and increase the FPS.
of.options.FAST_MATH.tooltip.6=This option can minimally affect the world generation.

of.options.CHUNK_UPDATES=Chunk Updates
of.options.CHUNK_UPDATES.tooltip.1=Chunk updates
of.options.CHUNK_UPDATES.tooltip.2= 1 - slower world loading, higher FPS (default)
of.options.CHUNK_UPDATES.tooltip.3= 3 - faster world loading, lower FPS
of.options.CHUNK_UPDATES.tooltip.4= 5 - fastest world loading, lowest FPS
of.options.CHUNK_UPDATES.tooltip.5=Number of chunk updates per rendered frame,
of.options.CHUNK_UPDATES.tooltip.6=higher values may destabilize the framerate.

of.options.CHUNK_UPDATES_DYNAMIC=Dynamic Updates
of.options.CHUNK_UPDATES_DYNAMIC.tooltip.1=Dynamic chunk updates
of.options.CHUNK_UPDATES_DYNAMIC.tooltip.2= OFF - standard chunk updates per frame (default)
of.options.CHUNK_UPDATES_DYNAMIC.tooltip.3= ON - more updates while the player is standing still
of.options.CHUNK_UPDATES_DYNAMIC.tooltip.4=Dynamic updates force more chunk updates while
of.options.CHUNK_UPDATES_DYNAMIC.tooltip.5=the player is standing still to load the world faster.

of.options.LAZY_CHUNK_LOADING=Lazy Chunk Loading
of.options.LAZY_CHUNK_LOADING.tooltip.1=Lazy Chunk Loading
of.options.LAZY_CHUNK_LOADING.tooltip.2= OFF - default server chunk loading
of.options.LAZY_CHUNK_LOADING.tooltip.3= ON - lazy server chunk loading (smoother)
of.options.LAZY_CHUNK_LOADING.tooltip.4=Smooths the integrated server chunk loading by
of.options.LAZY_CHUNK_LOADING.tooltip.5=distributing the chunks over several ticks.
of.options.LAZY_CHUNK_LOADING.tooltip.6=Turn it OFF if parts of the world do not load correctly.
of.options.LAZY_CHUNK_LOADING.tooltip.7=Effective only for local worlds (single-player).

of.options.RENDER_REGIONS=Render Regions
of.options.RENDER_REGIONS.tooltip.1=Render Regions
of.options.RENDER_REGIONS.tooltip.2= OFF - vanilla rendering (default)
of.options.RENDER_REGIONS.tooltip.3= ON - use render regions (faster)
of.options.RENDER_REGIONS.tooltip.4=Allows faster terrain rendering by optimizing
of.options.RENDER_REGIONS.tooltip.5=the GPU load. More effective at higher render distances.  
of.options.RENDER_REGIONS.tooltip.6=Not recommended for integrated graphics cards.

of.options.SMART_ANIMATIONS=Smart Animations
of.options.SMART_ANIMATIONS.tooltip.1=Smart Animations
of.options.SMART_ANIMATIONS.tooltip.2= OFF - do not use smart animations (default)
of.options.SMART_ANIMATIONS.tooltip.3= ON - use smart animations (faster)
of.options.SMART_ANIMATIONS.tooltip.4=With smart animations the game will only animate the 
of.options.SMART_ANIMATIONS.tooltip.5=textures which are currently visible on the screen.
of.options.SMART_ANIMATIONS.tooltip.6=This reduces the tick lag spikes and increases the FPS.
of.options.SMART_ANIMATIONS.tooltip.7=Especially useful for big mod packs and HD resource packs.

# Animations

of.options.animation.allOn=All ON
of.options.animation.allOff=All OFF
of.options.animation.dynamic=Dynamic

of.options.ANIMATED_WATER=Water Animated
of.options.ANIMATED_LAVA=Lava Animated
of.options.ANIMATED_FIRE=Fire Animated
of.options.ANIMATED_PORTAL=Portal Animated
of.options.ANIMATED_REDSTONE=Redstone Animated
of.options.ANIMATED_EXPLOSION=Explosion Animated
of.options.ANIMATED_FLAME=Flame Animated
of.options.ANIMATED_SMOKE=Smoke Animated
of.options.VOID_PARTICLES=Void Particles
of.options.WATER_PARTICLES=Water Particles
of.options.RAIN_SPLASH=Rain Splash
of.options.PORTAL_PARTICLES=Portal Particles
of.options.POTION_PARTICLES=Potion Particles
of.options.DRIPPING_WATER_LAVA=Dripping Water/Lava
of.options.ANIMATED_TERRAIN=Terrain Animated
of.options.ANIMATED_TEXTURES=Textures Animated
of.options.FIREWORK_PARTICLES=Firework Particles

# Other

of.options.LAGOMETER=Lagometer
of.options.LAGOMETER.tooltip.1=Shows the lagometer on the debug screen (F3).
of.options.LAGOMETER.tooltip.2=* Orange - Memory garbage collection
of.options.LAGOMETER.tooltip.3=* Cyan - Tick
of.options.LAGOMETER.tooltip.4=* Blue - Scheduled executables
of.options.LAGOMETER.tooltip.5=* Purple - Chunk upload
of.options.LAGOMETER.tooltip.6=* Red - Chunk updates
of.options.LAGOMETER.tooltip.7=* Yellow - Visibility check
of.options.LAGOMETER.tooltip.8=* Green - Render terrain

of.options.PROFILER=Debug Profiler
of.options.PROFILER.tooltip.1=Debug Profiler
of.options.PROFILER.tooltip.2=  ON - debug profiler is active, slower
of.options.PROFILER.tooltip.3=  OFF - debug profiler is not active, faster
of.options.PROFILER.tooltip.4=The debug profiler collects and shows debug information
of.options.PROFILER.tooltip.5=when the debug screen is open (F3).

of.options.WEATHER=Weather
of.options.WEATHER.tooltip.1=Weather
of.options.WEATHER.tooltip.2=  ON - weather is active, slower
of.options.WEATHER.tooltip.3=  OFF - weather is not active, faster
of.options.WEATHER.tooltip.4=The weather controls rain, snow and thunderstorms.
of.options.WEATHER.tooltip.5=Weather control is only possible for local worlds.

of.options.time.dayOnly=Day Only
of.options.time.nightOnly=Night Only

of.options.TIME=Time
of.options.TIME.tooltip.1=Time
of.options.TIME.tooltip.2= Default - normal day/night cycles
of.options.TIME.tooltip.3= Day Only - day only
of.options.TIME.tooltip.4= Night Only - night only
of.options.TIME.tooltip.5=The time setting is only effective in CREATIVE mode
of.options.TIME.tooltip.6=and for local worlds.

options.fullscreen.tooltip.1=Fullscreen
options.fullscreen.tooltip.2=  ON - use fullscreen mode
options.fullscreen.tooltip.3=  OFF - use window mode
options.fullscreen.tooltip.4=Fullscreen mode may be faster or slower than
options.fullscreen.tooltip.5=window mode, depending on the graphics card.

options.fullscreen.resolution=Fullscreen Mode
options.fullscreen.resolution.tooltip.1=Fullscreen mode
options.fullscreen.resolution.tooltip.2=  Default - use desktop screen resolution, slower
options.fullscreen.resolution.tooltip.3=  WxH - use custom screen resolution, may be faster
options.fullscreen.resolution.tooltip.4=The selected resolution is used in fullscreen mode (F11).
options.fullscreen.resolution.tooltip.5=Lower resolutions should generally be faster.

of.options.SHOW_FPS=Show FPS
of.options.SHOW_FPS.tooltip.1=Shows compact FPS and render information.
of.options.SHOW_FPS.tooltip.2=  Fps - average/minimum
of.options.SHOW_FPS.tooltip.3=  C: - chunk renderers
of.options.SHOW_FPS.tooltip.4=  E: - rendered entities + block entities
of.options.SHOW_FPS.tooltip.5=  U: - chunk updates
of.options.SHOW_FPS.tooltip.6=The compact FPS information is only shown when the
of.options.SHOW_FPS.tooltip.7=debug screen is not visible.

of.options.save.45s=45s
of.options.save.90s=90s
of.options.save.3min=3min
of.options.save.6min=6min
of.options.save.12min=12min
of.options.save.24min=24min

of.options.AUTOSAVE_TICKS=Autosave
of.options.AUTOSAVE_TICKS.tooltip.1=Autosave Interval
of.options.AUTOSAVE_TICKS.tooltip.2= 45s - default
of.options.AUTOSAVE_TICKS.tooltip.3=Autosave may generate lag spikes depending on the render distance.
of.options.AUTOSAVE_TICKS.tooltip.4=The world is also saved when the game menu is opened.

of.options.SCREENSHOT_SIZE=Screenshot Size
of.options.SCREENSHOT_SIZE.tooltip.1=Screenshot Size
of.options.SCREENSHOT_SIZE.tooltip.2=  Default - default screenshot size
of.options.SCREENSHOT_SIZE.tooltip.3=  2x-4x - custom screenshot size
of.options.SCREENSHOT_SIZE.tooltip.4=Capturing bigger screenshots may need more memory.
of.options.SCREENSHOT_SIZE.tooltip.5=Not compatible with Antialiasing.
of.options.SCREENSHOT_SIZE.tooltip.6=Requires GPU framebuffer support.

of.options.SHOW_GL_ERRORS=Show GL Errors
of.options.SHOW_GL_ERRORS.tooltip.1=Show OpenGL Errors
of.options.SHOW_GL_ERRORS.tooltip.2=When enabled OpenGL errors are shown in the chat.
of.options.SHOW_GL_ERRORS.tooltip.3=Disable it only if there is a known conflict and
of.options.SHOW_GL_ERRORS.tooltip.4=the errors can't be fixed.
of.options.SHOW_GL_ERRORS.tooltip.5=When disabled the errors are still logged in the 
of.options.SHOW_GL_ERRORS.tooltip.6=error log and they may still cause a significant FPS drop. 

# Chat Settings

of.options.CHAT_BACKGROUND=Chat Background
of.options.CHAT_BACKGROUND.tooltip.1=Chat Background
of.options.CHAT_BACKGROUND.tooltip.2=  Default - fixed width
of.options.CHAT_BACKGROUND.tooltip.3=  Compact - matches line width
of.options.CHAT_BACKGROUND.tooltip.4=  OFF - hidden

of.options.CHAT_SHADOW=Chat Shadow
of.options.CHAT_SHADOW.tooltip.1=Chat Shadow
of.options.CHAT_SHADOW.tooltip.2=  ON - use text shadow
of.options.CHAT_SHADOW.tooltip.3=  OFF - no text shadow
